messages.messageBody:
**That's him and he did writing for various magazines and stuff, I think. At
anyrate, I'm not giving my life history to some nut magazine just to read
the article. Guess I'll just have to keep wondering <g>**

You have to fill out the form in order to have access to the site, true. But
you aren't swearing to tell the truth, the whole truth, so help you g-d.

Heck, I even gave them true answers, just not useful ones.

Mom in the State of Chaos....... <g>
